      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/541936054_17945415186040233_4829697259602234995_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=102&amp;ig_cache_key=MzcxNDA4NjMzNzQxOTk1NTA2OQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=YJeBglNQiGMQ7kNvwFAyIaP&amp;_nc_oc=Adq6jmONSY8R8xnsLLhpmU89gzAjvRDTnkEG-4KB1Aw2osiRICviKLqMXTcKWZlJ6yQ&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=9P1h4LfN0GzWs3tHB8pI_A&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afx1M1tiUGuxHMOTwAy08pVsJ4qcRAMknBsJ7_tLCXEdfA&amp;oe=69CA0E62" alt="Slide 1 fra @caecilietrier" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/542741250_17945415195040233_865046574454287990_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_s1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=103&amp;ig_cache_key=MzcxNDA4NjMzNzE1MTUxNjI2Nw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=deR_8lu0EZIQ7kNvwHubm7v&amp;_nc_oc=AdqX-x7TkFRaFaCdGQ6yGXkLe7BXNFWoFyj98ruyb1xN39iVPlMFrAJ69a4azkCvjDA&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=9P1h4LfN0GzWs3tHB8pI_A&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwQKL0ou8LdhYrvhveg70UKbRHzJQzPzZ6AihpbicHLNA&amp;oe=69CA1335" alt="Slide 2 fra @caecilietrier" style="max-width: 48%; margin: 0 1% 8px 0;" /></p><p><strong>🖼️ Slideshow (2 medier)</strong></p><p><strong>@caecilietrier</strong></p><p>&#x27;Desire&#x27; by TLF Trio is out today in its entirety, the sophomore full-length album from the Danish group. We couldn&#x27;t be more happy &amp; honoured to release this one, and hope the music resonates with you. <br/>
<br/>
Composed, performed and produced by TLF Trio <br/>
Piano and synthesizer by Jakob Littauer <br/>
Guitar, sampler and synthesizer by MK Velsorf <br/>
Cello, synthesizer and piano by Cæcilie Trier <br/>
<br/>
Recorded at Rhythmic Music Conservatory, Copenhagen <br/>
Edited at Iconica Western, Los Angeles <br/>
Additional composition &amp; recording at KW Institute of Contemporary Art, Berlin &amp; The Wild Beast, California Institute of the Arts <br/>
<br/>
Engineered and pre-mixed by Nature Boy <br/>
Mixed by Aase Nielsen <br/>
Mastered by ET Mastering <br/>
Lacquer cut by Hari Kishore at Kommunal Dubplate Service, Copenhagen <br/>
<br/>
Cover photograph by Julia Sjölin <br/>
Graphic design by Atakan Kara<br/>
Supported by Koda Kultur</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DOLFdngDPAY/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
